skdetail:

Invocation Name: love calculator
des:
The Love Calculator is a fun way to check the compatibility of you and your significant other by comparing your names.
It will ask your first names and its algorythms will choose the results.
It will offer you the percentage chances for your relationship and offer you its opinion of it.
Have fun with it but just don't take it to seriously
